attributes.Long form description: The student unscrew the top hex socket heads of the table, from each side, using an Allen wrench. Then the student flip the table and withdraw all of the hex socket heads. Now, the student continue unscrewing the hex socket heads but now from the middle shelf of the table. Finally the student unscrew the last hex socket heads of the leg of the table, and separate all of the parts of the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first leg of the table.
